data.content:
Từ điển Anh - Việt
◘[,baiə'lɔdʒikəl]
 Cách viết khác:
 biologic
◘[,baiə'lɔdʒik]
 ■như biologic

Anh - Anh
biological
■ adjective
1》 relating to biology or living organisms.
    ⁃ (of a detergent) containing enzymes to assist the cleaning of washing.
2》 (of a parent or child) related by blood; natural.
3》 relating to or denoting the use of microorganisms or toxins of biological origin as weapons of war.
■ noun a biological product used for therapeutic purposes.
Derivatives
biologicadjective
biologicallyadverb

Từ điển Kỹ thuật (EN)
